high_descs: Walk up to the couch, then hang a right and walk over to the rightmost couch cushion.
Pick up the newspaper off of the rightmost couch cushion.
Turn left and begin walking forward, then hang a left and walk over to the fireplace, turn left to face the coffee table.
Place the newspaper on the closest corner of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk over to the middle seat cushion of the couch.
Pick up the newspaper off of the seat of the couch.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn left again and walk up to the fireplace, turn left to face the coffee table.
Place the newspaper on the coffee table to the left of the newspaper that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two newspapers to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn Right and go towards the end of couch.
Turn left to the couch pick up the newspaper from the corner seat.
Turn left and go forward and turn left  at the coffee table and stop at the end of coffee table.
Place the newspaper at the corner right side of the pencil on the coffee table.
Turn around and go back and then turn right and go towards the center seat of the couch.
Pick up the newspaper from the center seat.
Turn around and then turn left from the coffee table and stop at the corner of the coffee table.
Place the Newspaper on the coffee table the left side of the existing newspaper
anns.task_desc: Get the newspapers from Couch to the Coffee Table

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the newspaper on the right seat of the green couch.
Pick up the rightmost newspaper on the green couch.
Turn left and walk to the white table in front of the TV.
Place the newspaper down on the table on the corner closest to the fireplace.
Turn left and walk to the newspaper on the green couch.
Pick up the newspaper on the couch.
Turn around and walk to the white table in front of the TV.
Place the newspaper to the left of the other newspaper on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place two newspapers on the table in front of the TV.
